SINGING: Singing with trained skill

Category: Creative
Base skill: 30% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

A trained singing voice, well beyond an untrained character's
ability to carry a tune. Useful for performance, entertainment, or
simply making a strong impression in a social scene.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, dancing, play instrument, ventriloquism, art
